cs.HC, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.PL 

This paper is about improving the computational performance of constraint solvers for GUI layouts, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of constraints and solvers is also a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and simulation and modeling (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation of the solver in a programming language, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL).
